This repository holds functions relevant to spectral estimation of RBC policy functions and perturbation in Dynare.

The following function are modifications or supplied entirely by Jesus Fernandez-Villaverde (University of Pennsylvania, October 2013):
cheby_approx.m
chebyshev.m
col_points.m
nonlinear2.m (modification of nonlinear.m)

The rest were created by Kory Kantenga (University of Pennsylvania, 27 October 2013) in fullfillment of Homework 3 for Computation Economics.
